&lt;h1 class="mb-0 fade-in"&gt;Hi, I’m Dhwani&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="hero-subtitle fade-in"&gt;
  M.A. Candidate in Industrial & Organizational Psychology at NYU  
  &lt;br&gt;Bridging data and human insight to empower organizations
&lt;/div&gt;

Projects
Below are highlights of my consulting, research, and capstone work. Click “View PDF” to read the full document.




&lt;div class="card shadow-sm h-100"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
    &lt;h5 class="card-title"&gt;Boeing Cultural &amp; Leadership Transformation&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"&gt;Dec 2024&lt;/h6&gt;
    &lt;ul class="card-text" style="padding-left: 1rem;"&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Diagnosed leadership and cultural breakdowns after the 737 Max crashes—pinpointed “cost-saving over safety” and lack of transparency as core issues.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Proposed re-engineering Boeing’s mission, an internal ethics committee, and an overhauled leadership training program to rebuild employee trust.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Outlined measurable KPIs (e.g., safety-reporting compliance, 360-degree feedback scores) to track culture change and ethical accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;a href="projects/Boeing Proposal.pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank"&gt;
      View PDF
    &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;div class="card shadow-sm h-100"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
    &lt;h5 class="card-title"&gt;Listen Wellness: EAP Business Plan&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"&gt;Dec 2024&lt;/h6&gt;
    &lt;ul class="card-text" style="padding-left: 1rem;"&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Developed a full business plan targeting India’s manufacturing workforce, including market analysis and three pricing tiers (Basic, Standard, Premium).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Created operational roadmaps, marketing strategies, and financial projections seeking ₹50,00,000 in initial funding to launch in Gujarat.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Outlined service offerings (wellness assessments, workshops, crisis support) and a data-driven ROI framework (e.g., 20% reduction in absenteeism).&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;a href="projects/Business Project.pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank"&gt;
      View PDF
    &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;






&lt;div class="card shadow-sm h-100"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
    &lt;h5 class="card-title"&gt;Remote Work Professional Development Study&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"&gt;May 2024&lt;/h6&gt;
    &lt;ul class="card-text" style="padding-left: 1rem;"&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Surveyed 35 remote employees on factors (networking, training, engagement, motivation, demographics) affecting professional-development perceptions during COVID-19.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Ran descriptive stats, t-tests, ANOVA, correlation, and regression in R to identify that networking and mentoring strongly predicted perceived career growth.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Recommended virtual mentorship programs and structured feedback loops to mitigate isolation and enhance remote career support.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;a href="projects/Factors Affecting Employee Perceptions of Professional Development in a Remote Work Setting_DhwaniModi.pdf"
       class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank"&gt;
      View PDF
    &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;div class="card shadow-sm h-100"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
    &lt;h5 class="card-title"&gt;Dissertation: Work-Life Balance &amp; Turnover Intentions&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"&gt;May 2023&lt;/h6&gt;
    &lt;ul class="card-text" style="padding-left: 1rem;"&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Examined the impact of work-life balance factors on employee turnover intentions and identified factors causing job dissatisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Conducted descriptive statistics, ANOVA, correlation &amp; regression in Excel on survey data to evaluate the relationship between work-life balance and retention.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Presented actionable recommendations to reduce turnover &amp; improve organizational well-being through enhanced work-life initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;a href="projects/Impact of Work-Life Balance on Employee Turnover Intentions and Determining the Factors Causing Job Dissatisfaction.pdf"
       class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank"&gt;
      View PDF
    &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;






&lt;div class="card shadow-sm h-100"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
    &lt;h5 class="card-title"&gt;M&amp;A Case Study: GRS &amp; MejorVida&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"&gt;Nov 2023&lt;/h6&gt;
    &lt;ul class="card-text" style="padding-left: 1rem;"&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Analyzed cultural, leadership, and integration challenges when Global Retirement Strategies (GRS) acquired MejorVida in Chile.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Applied McKinsey’s cultural model—diagnosed “cultural distance” and designed a phased integration plan including alignment workshops and post-merger OD interventions.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Outlined “Red Team” coordination steps and 360-degree feedback mechanisms to ensure alignment between New York and Santiago offices.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;a href="projects/M&A case study.pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" target="_blank"&gt;
      View PDF
    &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
